      "policyLevel": "National",
      "policyOrigin": "Bureaucratic",
      "objectives": "<p>Owners who register fully electric cars will receive a rebate of 45 per cent off the Additional Registration Fee (ARF), capped at $20,000. This will narrow the upfront cost gap between electric and internal combustion engine cars.</p>",
