      "objectives": "<h4>Other sources</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wfw.com/articles/thailands-5-gw-renewable-ppa-fit-scheme-2022-2030/\">https://www.wfw.com/articles/thailands-5-gw-renewable-ppa-fit-scheme-2022-2030/</a><br><a href=\"https://www.iea.org/policies/5464-feed-in-tariff-for-distributed-solar-systems\">https://www.iea.org/policies/5464-feed-in-tariff-for-distributed-solar-systems</a></p>\n<p>The regulation, issued by Thailand's ERC, sets forth the Feed-in-Tariff (FiT) system for renewable energy projects selling electricity to state electricity authorities in Thailand until the year 2030.</p>",
